### Node ###
# Catch deps + build output anywhere in the repo. Per-app .gitignore files
# repeat these so they still work if this file is missing or moved.
node_modules/
dist/
build/
*.log
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
coverage/

### Secrets ###
# Never commit real env files. `.env.example` (no secrets, just keys) IS tracked.
.env
.env.local
.env.*.local
!.env.example

